vision.voltsofdoom.coresystem.loading.registry

Class FinalisedTypeRegistry<T extends IRegistryEntry<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • vision.voltsofdoom.coresystem.loading.registry.FinalisedTypeRegistry<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFinalisedRegistry<T>

    public class FinalisedTypeRegistry<T extends IRegistryEntry<T>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFinalisedRegistry<T>
    The finalised and immutable version of a TypeRegistry which will be added to the Registry. Still contains an IRegistryState, which is whilst being created, but is changed to once creation has finished.

      • lock

        public void lock()
        Description copied from interface: IFinalisedRegistry
        Is called by the Registry to close off this IFinalisedRegistry. This should ensure that no edits can be made to the contents of this IFinalisedRegistry after this method has been called. No need to (in fact, don't) call this method yourself, as this is dealt with by the game registry.
